aches, use a shield to prevent it.\n\n\u2022 How to proceed with the game\n1.Start\nOnce booted, system navigation will begin.\nTouch the Start-device to start.\n2.GamePlay\nIf you select Shikigami, the battle simulation will start after a while.", "short_description": "Pass-through MR shooting game.\nWelcome to Simulation X.\nPlease experience the power of Shikigami with MR."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.atsiaito.com/privacypolicy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "atsi_aito", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.atsiaito.com/product/simulationx", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["ACTION", "SHOOTER", "SIMULATION"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en", "ja"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH", "HAND_TRACKING"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "1180869906070795"}, "review_messages": ["", ""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982718_4823026774417245_7415700643551733224_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=TiToDiiS4HkQ7kNvgEw4BRu&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=Ao73W01_letdAsmESwv9dlB&oh=00_AYDrNMEI6_a0nR1k2eAFLWtJjs9PgAsMPRFxyUvukzcdcQ&oe=66F55C89"}, "is_concept": false, "is_test": false, "is_trial_offer_valid": false, "display_name": "Simulation X trial", "platform": "ANDROID_6DOF", "context_category": null, "context_topics": [], "release_date": 1653665493, "lastRevision": {"nodes": [{"id": "653335429307675", "rele